            <title>[LU-7167] sanity-scrub test_4b: test failed to respond and timed out</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7167</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Bob Glossman &amp;lt;bob.glossman@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/0ca3c092-5b65-11e5-97bd-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/0ca3c092-5b65-11e5-97bd-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_4b failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;test failed to respond and timed out
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;seen during el7 client/server test on master&lt;br/&gt;
don&apos;t yet know if it&apos;s reproducible or only a one-off&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity-scrub 4b&lt;/p&gt;</description>
